      <li><p><em>Register</em> varies by tenor (relationship), field (subject), and mode (channel).</p></li>
      <li><p><em>Formal register</em> uses standard grammar, complete forms, and impersonal constructions.</p></li>
      <li><p><em>Informal register</em> uses contractions, simple structures, and personal tone.</p></li>
